author: Unity
description:
Excited for Unite, but unable to make it all the way to Barcelona? Join us for a conversational, community-centric livestream featuring developers, Unity guests, session info, and more!

This is day 2 and we will officially start at 11AM CET (Barcelona local time), or 2AM PT / 5AM ET / 7PM JST.
title: Unite 2025 Community Hangout - Day 2 Live From Barcelona

author: Unity
description:
Build profiles are Unity 6's new configuration management system that streamlines application development across multiple platforms. Rather than reconfiguring settings for each build target manually, you can create and save platform-specific configurations as reusable profiles, and get more efficient cross-platform development workflows.

Watch our full tutorial here: https://on.unity.com/BuildProfileTutorial

Learn more in docs: https://on.unity.com/BuildProfileDocs 

Find more free Unity learn resources: https://on.unity.com/learn

#gamedev #unitytips #unity3d #unitylearn
title: Unity 6 tips: Build profiles #gamedev #unitytips #gamedevelopment
